{"tid":1418361,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我係一個經常發夢嘅道路使用者，有少少睇法想同大家分享","createTime":"2019-08-05T18:31:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T13:34:07.000Z","uid":62811,"like":27,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a8b0b169c45095a9a79497ebc930d5ad7792f261","tid":1418361,"uid":62811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:31:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">人畜有別 BE WATER, BE HUMBLE</span></span><br />\n<br />\n發夢嗰時經常要塞路<br />\n其實好多司機到呢一刻都係支持緊我地，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但係大家要明白呢樣野唔會永遠發生，終有一日會變成或被抹黑成擾民</span></span><br />\n建議可以多啲視乎情況開返<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">一條行車線</span></span>有限度行車或者有秩序咁比一啲受困嘅車輛慢慢離場，既可以做到塞車效果影響狗隻支援時間，又可以爭取返啲道路使用者嘅支持(<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">唔好同我講民意無用，唔係邊得嚟咁多車手運物資 / 咁多家長接放學 / 咁多人係迴旋處練車個</span></span>)<br />\n<br />\n又或者好似今日快閃紅隧咁，手足走哂就讓返條路出嚟，遞個手講聲唔好意思。<br />\n<br />\n引用梁天琦曾經講過嘅句說話<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">得民心者 得天下</span></span>"},{"pid":"b0ed45c87ac9d97e230667afd6e67c1b2152acb6","tid":1418361,"uid":62811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:51:41.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"d223174861337d60b6c502e3acd859337631be63","tid":1418361,"uid":62811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:40:17.000Z","msg":"時代革命"},{"pid":"7cc2f0f73b89bf349f1c8e49c83f5041cb393325","tid":1418361,"uid":138740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:47:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"00012c3892ff77a9c1dfe4ff7874304d072022c3","tid":1418361,"uid":228437,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:49:42.000Z","msg":"其實係，有多一條線俾車行，物資都易入啲<br />\n俾人屌少好多"},{"pid":"da92f770cf5b171838d6930fac5265ca4f0b881e","tid":1418361,"uid":233325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:57:16.000Z","msg":"俾前線睇"},{